    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How long does it take to sell a home in Brookfield?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Well-presented Brookfield acreage typically sells within 45 to 75 days. The buyer pool is smaller than for suburban Brisbane but is consistently well qualified, with strong representation from upgraders out of Kenmore, Chapel Hill and Indooroopilly. Premium homes positioned well at launch can transact faster." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the lifestyle like in Brookfield?",
