════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2ead4); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Acreage with a village heart.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Brookfield is the western acreage suburb that has retained a true village core. The Brookfield General Store, the showgrounds and the school sit at the centre of the suburb, and most of the residential acreage radiates out from this hub. The combination of rural-residential land, a walkable village heart and a 25 minute drive to the CBD is genuinely uncommon in Brisbane, and the suburb has built a distinctive community identity around it.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
<div style="background:#fff; border-left:4px solid #b98229; padding:2rem 2rem 1.75rem; margin:2rem 0; border-radius:16px;">
  <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Free Appraisal</p>
